### Slide 10: Ask/Next Steps

**Purpose:** Clear call to action and next milestones

**What to Include:**
- Specific ask (if raising money)
- What the resources will achieve
- Next 6-12 month milestones
- Call to action

**Structure:**

```
Next Steps

[If raising money:]
The Ask:
â€¢ Amount: $XXX
â€¢ Use: [Specific allocation]
â€¢ Outcomes: [What you'll achieve]

[Always include:]
Next 6 Months:
â€¢ Month 1-2: [Milestone]
â€¢ Month 3-4: [Milestone]
â€¢ Month 5-6: [Milestone]

Contact:
[Email]
[Website/Demo link]

Call to Action:
[What you want from audience]
```

**Example - Good (Raising Money):**

```
The Ask: $50K Seed Funding

Use of Funds:
â€¢ $25K: Product Development (2 developers, 4 months)
â€¢ $15K: User Acquisition (Instagram ads, campus ambassadors)
â€¢ $10K: University Partnerships (travel, pilot programs)

This Gets Us To:
â€¢ 2,000 active users across 3 universities
â€¢ $15K MRR (Monthly Recurring Revenue)
â€¢ Ready for Series A conversation

Next 6 Months:
â€¢ Jan-Feb: Launch at KIU, target 500 users
â€¢ Mar-Apr: Expand to Tbilisi universities  
â€¢ May-Jun: Hit profitability milestone

Contact: team@campusconnect.ge
Demo: app.campusconnect.ge

Let's connect to discuss partnership opportunities!
```

**Example - Good (Not Raising Money):**

```
Next Steps: Launching January 2025

Q1 2025 Milestones:
â€¢ January: Public launch at KIU
  Target: 500 active users, 15% premium conversion
  
â€¢ February: Expand to 3 Tbilisi universities
  Target: 1,500 total users
  
â€¢ March: Enterprise partnerships
  Target: 5 university departments as paid customers

What We Need:
â€¢ Introductions to university administrators
â€¢ Beta testers from your networks  
â€¢ Feedback and mentorship

Contact: team@campusconnect.ge
Try it: app.campusconnect.ge

We're building the future of university life. Join us!
```

**Example - Bad:**

```
Next Steps

We need money to grow.

We'll get more users and make it better.

Contact us if interested.
```

**Why Bad Example Fails:**
- Vague ask
- No specific milestones
- No resource allocation
- Weak call to action

**Types of Asks:**

**For Student Projects:**
- âœ… Feedback and mentorship
- âœ… Beta testers
- âœ… Introductions to potential users/partners
- âœ… Technical guidance
- âœ… Future employment opportunities

**For Real Startups:**
- âœ… Specific funding amount
- âœ… Strategic partnerships
- âœ… Advisory board members
- âœ… Pilot customers
- âœ… Next round intros

**Your Ask/Next Steps Checklist:**
- [ ] Specific ask (money, intros, feedback)
- [ ] Clear use of resources
- [ ] Measurable milestones
- [ ] Timeline with dates
- [ ] Contact information
- [ ] Compelling call to action

