## Examples & Case Studies

### Excellent Pitch Decks (Study These)

**Airbnb (2009 Seed Round)**
- Simple, clear problem (expensive hotels)
- Photos of actual product
- Traction with revenue numbers
- Clear business model

**Dropbox (2007 Seed Round)**
- Video demo (brilliant for file sync)
- Clear market size calculation
- Simple value proposition
- Technical moat explained simply

**Buffer (2011 Seed Round)**
- Transparent metrics
- Clear validation (paying customers)
- Simple, beautiful design
- Evidence-driven story

### What They All Have in Common

âœ… Tell a clear story  
âœ… Show, don't just tell  
âœ… Use real data  
âœ… Simple, clean design  
âœ… Focus on customer problem  

